{"tid":1561491,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"免費幫各位義士整iPhone主板","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:16:58.000Z","uid":164378,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b545299766583c99ab64528b8fbb077d6b03c4","tid":1561491,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:25:59.000Z","msg":"代POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢位朋友P牌仔，個POST推唔郁，幫手係呢度推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1559974/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1559974/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n呢三個月眼見各位義士為香港付出好多，好多人搞到自己無錢食飯，甚至要走佬去台灣，令我好感動<br />\n但我自問又無乜錢捐出黎，又自問無前線咁勇武<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我決定出個post ，做番我既專長，<span style=\"color: red;\">幫大家免費整iPhone </span> 無論係前線既義士，後排支援既義士，甚至只係精神上支持既巴絲，<span style=\"color: red;\">一律都係免費</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想整機既巴絲可以ig或tg聯絡我<br />\nIg:iPhonemotherboardhk<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/IphoneMotherboardhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FIphoneMotherboardhk&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=c8e4f57f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/IphoneMotherboardhk</a>"},{"pid":"355ea502c44268065c156aff528632e7e26847d6","tid":1561491,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>